\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa200\ql\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 [10]\tab  Glaze is a vitreous coating used on ceramic products such as tiles and sanitary ware.   It is made out of a mixture of frit and various other materials such as silica, clay, calcium carbonate and others.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\sl240\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs25\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 For presentation on how ceramics are manufactured.  See: pgs 568 -572 of the merger record}}}
