\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa200\ql\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 [25]\tab Ferro\'92s status in the glaze market was uncertain at the time that this matter was heard.  At the pre-hearing the Tribunal was advised that Ferro was planning to exit the glaze market irrespective of the outcome of this inquiry.  However, its presence 
