\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa200\ql\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 [26]\tab  Mr Kromm testified that he was unaware of Ferro\'92s exit from the glaze market and that he was under the impression that they were still supplying glaze to the tile industry.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\sl240\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs25\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch   }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 Mr Kroom\'92s evidence on Pg. 116 of the transcript}}}
{\*\cs25\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up9\rtlch\af9\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af7\langfe255\hich\f0\fs24\lang1033\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033\rtlch\af2\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 }{\rtlch\af2\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2   Mr Ian Forbes on behalf of Ferro testified that Ferro was simply complying 
