\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa200\ql\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 [43]\tab Mr Forbes did not explain the intention behind clause 10.4 but testified that despite the existence of clause 10.4 there was no intention to supply frit to Spectrum at inflated prices.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\sl240\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs25\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 It is possible that that clause 10.4 was initially drafted to provide that Ferro would provide Spectrum with frit in accordance with that formula but was later amended to include Mrs Alegra\'92s views.}}}
