\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\sl276\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sa200\ql\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang1033\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang1033\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 [50]\tab   While Smalticeram harboured the hope of concluding a supply agreement with CIL, it was uncertain whether this would happen.   Even if we were to assume that entry was likely it hardly seemed timely or sufficient to compete effectively with the merge
